Unsigned char 	8	1	0-255
Signed char	8	1	-128---127
Unsigned int 	16	2	0-65536
Signed int	16	2	-32768-----32767
Unsigned long	32	4	0---4*109
Signed long	32	4	2*10-9 -----------2*109
Folat	32	4	1*10-38 -----------2*1038
Double	64	8	1*10-38 -----------2*1038
一般指针	24	3	
